controller

Class GoLController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.GoLController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class GoLController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    GoLController handles all user inputs. Sending userinputs to their destination. Containing all controller instances from the GoL.fxml file.

      • loadFileBtnClicked

        public void loadFileBtnClicked()
                        throws java.io.IOException,
                               PatternFormatException
        LoadFileBtnClicked() allows the user to load a RLE pattern from a file on "Load file" button clicked.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - IOException is thrown if something went wrong during file reading. A dialog is shown to the user.
        PatternFormatException - is thrown if there is something wrong with the file content. A dialog is shown to the user.

      • loadURLBtnClicked

        public void loadURLBtnClicked()
                       throws java.io.IOException,
                              PatternFormatException
        LoadURLBtnClicked() allows the user to load a RLE pattern from a URL on "Load url" button clicked.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - IOException is thrown if something went wrong during URL reading. A dialog is shown to the user.
        PatternFormatException - is thrown if there is something wrong with the URL content. A dialog is shown to the user.

      • keyEventScene

        public void keyEventScene(javafx.scene.input.KeyEvent e)
        Key listener that allows the user to move a loaded RLE/URL pattern around the canvas. And place it where he/she desiers. It is also possible to rotate the loaded pattern. It also allows the user to move the generation around in zoomed mode, by using the arrow keys.
        Parameters:
        e - e KeyEvent, listening to user input on the canvas.

      • autoAdjustCanvas

        public void autoAdjustCanvas()
